                                                rdfs:label "Has Canadian organization taxation status"@en .


###  https://csse.utoronto.ca/has_concession_information
bedeo:has_concession_information rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
                                 rdfs:domain bedeo:Address ,
                                             bedeo:Location ;
                                 rdfs:range xsd:string ;
                                 rdfs:comment """A concession is a row of lots within a township, typically running parallel to each other and separated by road allowances (e.g. Concession 9)

Example:

Application B 22/16 Part of Lots 32-36, Con 2 Sidney, Now Belleville
Owner: Robert Jakes, Jenland Properties Ltd.
Agent: Keith Watson, Watson Land Surveyors Ltd.

Township: Sidney
Concession: 2
Lots: 32 to 36""" ;
                                 rdfs:label "Has concession information"@en .


